trans-unit.source: One or more users are not assigned to the same Business Central license. For example, we found that users %1 and %2 are assigned to different licenses, but there may be other mismatches. In your Microsoft 365 admin center, make sure that all users are assigned to the same Business Central license, either Basic, Essential, or Premium. Afterward, update Business Central by opening the Users page and using the 'Update Users from Office 365' action.
